entries.s_58: Excuse me, you are the person that will take me to Officer Ten'doora, are you not?
entries.s_60: Yes, I'm here to take you to him.
entries.s_62: The plans have changed.  The information that I have is very time sensitive and I'll only slow you down.  You need to get to Officer Ten'doora within 20 minutes and give him this message:  Droids need Star Destroyers in the evening.
entries.s_64: Droids need Star Destroyers in the evening?  You have to be kidding me.
entries.s_66: Do you think that I'm risking my life out here for nothing?  Just tell him what I said and don't screw it up.  Time is ticking.
entries.s_68: Got it.  I'm on my way.
entries.s_72: Why are you standing around, get moving!
entries.s_74: Can't a person just enjoy a lovely day?  Please leave me be.
